    "body": "Hi!\nThe TRACE APIs are only for getting trace-level details of existing transactions, this doesn't enable you to do any restricting or rejecting of activity. \n\nIt sounds like what you want (privileges) might be role based access - this can be implemented at the application layer eg https://docs.openzeppelin.com/contracts/2.x/access-control#role-based-access-control\n\n",
